<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7822612>
    dc:description "FIG. 11. — Heteroscyphus deplanchei (Steph.) Schiffn.: A, shoot portion, ventral view; B, leaf cells; C, K, leaf apices diversity; D, leaf; E, shoot portion, dorsal view; F, female bract; G, androecium, dorsal view; H, pair of male bracts and bracteole, dorsal view; I, leaf and underleaf; J, perianth open with calyptra (ca). A, B, drawn from the holotype of Chiloscyphus deplanchei Steph. (G00069487); C-F, J, from Thouvenot NC2852; G, H, from Thouvenot NC2773; I, K, from the type of Lophocolea heteromorphis Steph. (G00112505). Scale bars: A, C-F, I-K, 1 mm; B, 50 µm; G, 400 µm; H, 200 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7822612/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

